; DX blurbs
(alterna_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "A fan of roller derby and distorted feedback, Judy Nails has been a pioneer of alternative rock since her first tour at age 17. Known for her diverse collection of LP's, Nails brings an experimental twist to heavy guitar riffs with a sly smirk."
      "A fan of distorted feedback and roller derby, Judy Nails has been a pioneer of alt-rock since her first tour at age 17. Known for her huge collection of vinyl, Judy brings a smile, and a lot of pedals, to the stage."})
(classic_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "Having abandoned his fascination with the sitar, an interest developed during a 3-year, court-ordered \qmeditation retreat,\q Winston sashays boldly back to the forefront of classic rock with his guitar wizardry and iconic status."
      "Having abandoned his fascination with the sitar (an interest developed during a court-ordered \qmeditation retreat\q), Clive returns to the forefront of classic rock with his guitar wizardry and iconic status."})
(deathmetal_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "Lock the doors and board the windows, Lars Ümlaüt is soon to storm a town near you. An intimidating presence, the Norwegian-born Ümlaüt describes himself as \qa force for you to be doing the reckoning with!\q"
      "Lock the doors and board the windows, Lars Ümlaüt is coming for you! An intimidating presence, the Norwegian-born Ümlaüt describes himself as \qa force for you to be doing the reckoning with!\q"})
(funk1_blurb "Raised in suburban Connecticut, Xavier Stone broke from his pampered upbringing after realizing he preferred rock clubs to country clubs. Weaving slick '70s style with chunky grooves, Xavier does it right every time.")
(goth_blurb "Pandora's youth is shrouded in mystery. Some say she was born in a dimension of pure darkness. Others say she was raised in a duplex near Boise. With her blazing solos and chaotic melodies, Pandora is the Dark Princess of Rock.")
(glam_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "A real crowd pleaser, Hair thrills all with his energetic onstage showmanship while delighting the media with his offstage debauchery. Hair's fan base is even bigger than, well, his hair."
      "A real crowd pleaser, Izzy thrills all with his energetic onstage showmanship while delighting the media with his offstage debauchery. Izzy's fan base is even bigger than his hair."})
(grim_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "This rock star is bad to the bone. Grim's riffs are so huge, fans are lucky just to leave the show with their souls intact. At his latest killer performance, an awestruck fan gushed, \qThe curtains flew, then he appeared!\q"
      "This rock star is bad to the bone. Grim's riffs are so killer, fans are lucky just to leave the show with their souls intact. Grim's supernatural licks always knock 'em dead. 'Cause he's...you know...right."})
(metal_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "Famous for his driving riffs and up-front attitude, Hazzard first picked up a guitar in an attempt to quell his boredom during suspension from elementary school. The rest is history. Metal history."
      "Famous for his driving riffs and up-front attitude, Axel Steel first picked up a guitar in an attempt to quell his boredom during suspension from elementary school. The rest is history. Metal history."})
(punk_blurb "Johnny embodies the true spirit of punk rock with his signature stomp and swagger. Released from lockup for \qalmost tolerable behavior,\q Johnny lurches back into the spotlight, rough and ready for action.")
(rock_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "A veteran of the tour circuit, Gina's dirty, bass-driven sound and ultra-heavy riffs have influenced budding shredders from Maine to Alaska. She's tough, she's brash, and she'll break your heart faster than an A string."
      "A veteran of the tour circuit, Casey's dirty, low-end growl and ultra-heavy riffs have influenced budding shredders from Maine to Alaska. She's tough, she's brash, and she'll break your heart faster than an E string."})
(rockabill_blurb
   {if_else $egg5
      "When he's not cruisin' around Reno in his '53 Ford, Dax Deville brings his brand of hard-working rock to any stage he sets foot on. A real \qroad dog,\q Deville claims that as long as he's got his hollow body and a tin of pomade, he \qain't too far from home.\q"
      "When he's not cruisin' in his '55 Chevy, Eddie brings his hard-working rock to any stage he sets foot on. A real \qroad dog,\q Eddie Knox claims that as long as he's got his hollow body and his pomade, he \qain't too far from home.\q"})
(streamer_blurb "Emerging from shadows after a 28 hour marathon live stream, Streamer brings forth the gift of darkness to those who check the link in the description. Also don't forget to follow and subscribe.")

